class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="habitat-noosa" class="entry-website-title">Habitat Noosa</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-habitat-noosa-20240526-desktop.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-habitat-noosa-20240526-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-habitat-noosa-20240526-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Habitat Noosa"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://habitatnoosa.com.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://habitatnoosa.com.au/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Noosa, Queensland, Australia</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Habitat Noosa Everglades Eco Camp is an award-winning camping site near Noosa, Australia. The campsite offers a variety of accommodation options, including camping, glamping, and cabins.</p><p>Visitors can easily find information about accommodation, activities, sustainability efforts, and booking. However, much of the website content is hidden behind the "MORE" menu, including the blog, park map, and park rules. A standout feature is the sustainability section, where visitors can learn how to offset their carbon footprint when traveling to the location.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The site includes a sustainability section with quick info about carbon offsetting. The site also includes a blog and a digital brochure. Gift vouchers are available to purchase. The site has a chatbot for assistance.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>Some of the pages are text-heavy and slow to load which some readers might find distracting. Too much of the site content is hidden behind the "More" menu button where the site could have introduced individual pages. WAVE picked up a few contrast errors on the home page.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-habitat-noosa-20240526-desktop.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-habitat-noosa-20240526-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop website looks spectacular, with expansive high-quality images dominating the home page and accommodation pages. The "Book Now" button is always present in the sticky top menu for quick bookings and the chatbot pops up intermittently but is easily closed. While the site is generally quite fast, we found some of the pages loaded slowly. The desktop site scored 74/100 on Google's PageSpeed Insights test.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-habitat-noosa-20240526-mobile.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-habitat-noosa-20240526-mobile.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The mobile website maintains the overall aesthetic and functionality, retaining the high-quality images on the home page. While the sticky top menu converts into a hamburger menu, it quickly loses the CTA booking button when scrolling, which seems like an oversight. In real-world tests, many of the pages felt slow to load as confirmed by the Google PageSpeed performance score of 30/100.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
class="entry-container entry-container-content"><div
class="entry-content-wrapper"><div
class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="tathra-beach-eco-camp" class="entry-website-title">Tathra Beach Eco Camp</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-tahra-eco-camp-20240526-desktop.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-tahra-eco-camp-20240526-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-tahra-eco-camp-20240526-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Tathra Beach Eco Camp"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://tathraecocamp.com.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://tathraecocamp.com.au/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Tathra, New South Wales, Australia</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Tathra Beach Eco Camp is an eco-friendly campsite nestled in the bushland adjacent to Tathra Beach in New South Wales. The company offers a variety of accommodations, including camping, glamping, and cabins.</p><p>The website has a nature-inspired theme, with high-quality scrolling images of families enjoying the natural environment. The layout is well thought out and organized into clear sections for accommodation, activities, and booking options. The embedded YouTube video on the home page is a nice touch for visitors who want to know more about the campsite.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The home page has an embedded YouTube video showcasing the campsite and its various facilities. The scrolling videos on the home page add visual appeal yet don't slow down the performance of the site. An accessibility scan of the site showed very few errors.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>There are no customer reviews on the website which is an oversight since most visitors will want to know what other people think about the campsite. Pricing is only available when booking accommodation.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-tahra-eco-camp-20240526-desktop.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-tahra-eco-camp-20240526-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The larger screen size on the desktop website aids in showcasing the spectacular visuals of the campsite. While many of the pages are slow to load, we felt they were within acceptable real-world limits. While the site has three separate CTA booking buttons, none of them are particularly prominent. The desktop site scored 49/100 on Google's PageSpeed Insights test for performance but fared better on SEO and best practices.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-tahra-eco-camp-20240526-mobile.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-tahra-eco-camp-20240526-mobile.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>While functional, the mobile website has slow loading times, and some of the images get cut off or overlaid by previous images. The top menu also disappears when scrolling, making navigation difficult.</p><p>Unlike the desktop site, the mobile version includes a prominent search function in the top menu. The site received a score of 31/100 on PageSpeed Insights, confirming the slow loading times found in real-world tests.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
class="entry-container entry-container-content"><div
class="entry-content-wrapper"><div
class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="stoats-farm" class="entry-website-title">Stoats Farm</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-stoats-farm-20240605-desktop.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-stoats-farm-20240605-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-stoats-farm-20240605-desktop.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Stoats Farm"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
