class="entry-text"><p>Stoats Farm is a quiet, family- and dog-friendly campsite on the Isle of Wight, offering facilities like holiday lets and glamping. The website greets visitors with an impressive full-scale background image of the isle, with an information block and a quick book button. There is also a small image gallery for a snapshot of what to expect.</p><p>From the top menu, visitors can access information about pricing, online bookings, and information about the Isle of Wight. Notable features include downloadable directions and booking terms and conditions. While all pertinent information is available, the website is missing links to online reviews.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
