class="entry-content"><div
class="entry-content-section"><h3 id="casini-ranch-family-campground" class="entry-website-title">Casini Ranch Family Campground</h3><div
class="entry-website-img"><div
class="entry-faux-browser"><div
class="entry-browser-menu"><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div><div
class="dot"></div></div>
<picture>
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-casini-ranch-desktop-3840x10061-2024064.webp?crop=2:1,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=332&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 412px)" />
<source
data-srcset="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-casini-ranch-desktop-3840x10061-2024064.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=495&dpr=2" media="(max-width: 575px)" />
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-casini-ranch-desktop-3840x10061-2024064.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=650&dpr=2"
width="650"
height="403"
alt="desktop screenshot of website Casini Ranch Family Campground"
/>
</picture></div></div><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-url">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-link.svg" alt="chain icon" width="29" height="29" />
</span>
<a
class="force-single-line" href="https://casiniranch.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
https://casiniranch.com/
</a></p><p
class="entry-website-detail website-detail-location">
<span
class="icon">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-pin.svg" alt="pin icon" width="30" height="30" />
</span>
<span>Duncans Mills, California, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Casini Ranch Family Campground, located in the Russian River Valley, offers a variety of accommodations including RV sites, tent sites, and cabins. It is a family- and pet-friendly destination with riverfront access.</p><p>Casini Ranch goes to great lengths to ensure their images take center stage on the website, opting for text overlays instead of a solid top menu. To complement the large image banner, the site includes a promotional YouTube video, innovative 360 virtual tour, and interactive map. A nice feature is the web accessibility button at the bottom of the page.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The website includes a 360 virtual tour and an information video. There is an interactive campsite map. There is a dedicated page for pricing and testimonials. Web accessibility options are provided.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>WAVE reported a number of contrast errors on the site. When clicking on the information video, the stream lagged or didn't play. Sometimes clicking on the video opens the virtual 3D tour instead.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-casini-ranch-desktop-3840x10061-2024064.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-casini-ranch-desktop-3840x10061-2024064.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The desktop site uses the full width of the screen to showcase the breathtaking scenery of the campsite. The menu does not float down the page though, which is an oversight that could be fixed with a sticky menu or a back-to-top button. The desktop website scored 52/100 on the PageSpeed Insights test, confirming the slightly slow loading times seen in our real-world test.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-casini-ranch-mobile-824x13226-2024064.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-casini-ranch-mobile-824x13226-2024064.webp?crop=3:5,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=375&dpr=2"
alt="mobile screenshot of website"
width="325"
height="542"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>The mobile website offers a similar experience with dominant images and a small hamburger menu that doesn't float when scrolling. We also found that the 360 virtual tour video lagged on mobile.</p><p>The mobile website received a score of 30/100 for performance on PageSpeed Insights but fared better on SEO and accessibility. In our real-world tests, we found the mobile experience to be acceptable.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
